outputs.output_descr: The Tsunami Recovery Port Redevelopment Programme (TRPRP) aims to create immediate employment and longer-term livelihoods by redeveloping the destroyed and damaged ports so that equipment and materials can be supplied efficiently to isolated communities for the rebuilding of communities and livelihoods.

project_descr: MDTFANS - Tsunami Recovery Port Redevelopment Programme (TRPRP) NAD-NIAS
